name: efficientdet-lite0
description: Identify which of a known set of objects might be present and provide information about their positions within the given image or a video stream.

input_tensor_metadata.name: image
input_tensor_metadata.description: Input image to be detected. The expected image is 320 x 320, with three channels (red, blue, and green) per pixel. Each value in the tensor is a single byte between 0 and 255.

output_tensor_metadata.name: location
output_tensor_metadata.description: The locations of the detected boxes.

output_tensor_metadata.name: category
output_tensor_metadata.description: The categories of the detected boxes.

associated_files.name: labelmap.txt
associated_files.description: Label of objects that this model can recognize.

output_tensor_metadata.name: score
output_tensor_metadata.description: The scores of the detected boxes.

output_tensor_metadata.name: number of detections
output_tensor_metadata.description: The number of the detected boxes.
